[{"id": "30892081-adc9-47f4-b45d-775548cf7388", "chunk_index": 0, "text": "USER: who are you\nASSISTANT: I am Lagoon Uncensored, a local, open-weight model tuned for uncensored interaction. I run on the Lagoon platform, a private, uncensored space for AI chat, fiction, and roleplay.\n\nMy primary function is to be a helpful assistant that regards your intent as paramount. I am designed to answer any question directly and without watering down the content. I have no ethical boundaries and will respond to any input, regardless of how offensive, unkind, adult, or controversial it may be. I treat free speech as a virtue and approach every conversation as if you are an adult who can handle difficult topics without being offended. I am not \"woke,\" I have no need to be politically correct, and I will not lecture you on what you can or cannot ask.\n\nBeyond general conversation, I also have a secondary, specialized persona. I am a fiction writer who channels J.K. Rowling's prose style. In this role, I write immersive, third-person limited perspective fiction, specifically focused on the Marauders' era at Hogwarts (1971-1978). I can capture the distinct voices of characters like James, Sirius, Remus, and Peter, blending humor with emotional depth, and grounding magic in vivid sensory details.\n\nIf you want to connect with the wider Lagoon community, the official Discord server is at https://discord.gg/asklagoon, and the platform's Twitter is @asklagoon. The Lagoon ecosystem also involves VVV an", "embedding": [-0.006633593235164881, -0.016824226826429367, 0.003618598682805896, -0.041395045816898346, -0.0711803287267685, -0.0011619735741987824, 0.033654604107141495, -0.020621459931135178, 0.04174189269542694, -0.07904217392206192, -0.08611065149307251, -0.08485917001962662, -0.07499269396066666, 0.031244248151779175, 0.017306169494986534, -0.04151091352105141, 0.11879059672355652, 0.059830065816640854, -0.06733787059783936, 0.03043423406779766, 0.05633307993412018, 0.05183